(43, 5, 30, 40, 26, 39, 39, NULL, 'Submission to God''s Will', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of seeking God''s will over personal desires. In John 5:30, Jesus states he seeks the will of the Father, while in Matthew 26:39, he expresses a desire for the Father''s will to prevail over his own.', 'theme', 0.43999999999999995, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini')
